{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.1","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:1","prev_osis_id":"Acts.005.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Institution des diacres<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. Ex 18:13-26. 1 Ti 3:8-13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>En ce temps-l\u00e0, le nombre des disciples augmentant, les Hell\u00e9nistes murmur\u00e8rent contre les H\u00e9breux, parce que leurs veuves \u00e9taient n\u00e9glig\u00e9es dans la distribution qui se faisait chaque jour.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.2","name":"Actes 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.5.42","name":"Actes 5:42","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.5.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.2","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:2","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Les douze convoqu\u00e8rent la multitude des disciples, et dirent: Il n\u2019est pas convenable que nous laissions la parole de Dieu pour servir aux tables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.3","name":"Actes 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.1","name":"Actes 6:1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.3","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:3","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, fr\u00e8res, choisissez parmi vous sept hommes, de qui l\u2019on rende un bon t\u00e9moignage, qui soient pleins d\u2019Esprit-Saint et de sagesse, et que nous chargerons de cet emploi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.4","name":"Actes 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.2","name":"Actes 6:2","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.4","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:4","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et nous, nous continuerons \u00e0 nous appliquer \u00e0 la pri\u00e8re et au minist\u00e8re de la parole.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.5","name":"Actes 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.3","name":"Actes 6:3","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.5","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:5","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Cette proposition plut \u00e0 toute l\u2019assembl\u00e9e. Ils \u00e9lurent \u00c9tienne, homme plein de foi et d\u2019Esprit-Saint, Philippe, Prochore, Nicanor, Timon, Parm\u00e9nas, et Nicolas, pros\u00e9lyte d\u2019Antioche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.6","name":"Actes 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.4","name":"Actes 6:4","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.6","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:6","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Ils les pr\u00e9sent\u00e8rent aux ap\u00f4tres, qui, apr\u00e8s avoir pri\u00e9, leur impos\u00e8rent les mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.7","name":"Actes 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.5","name":"Actes 6:5","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.7","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:7","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">\u00c9tienne accus\u00e9 de blasph\u00e8me, traduit devant le sanh\u00e9drin, et lapid\u00e9 par les Juifs<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-15: cf. H\u00e9 2:4. Lu 21:14, 15. Jn 15:18-21.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\n    La parole de Dieu se r\u00e9pandait de plus en plus, le nombre des disciples augmentait beaucoup \u00e0 J\u00e9rusalem, et une grande foule de sacrificateurs ob\u00e9issaient \u00e0 la foi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.8","name":"Actes 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.6","name":"Actes 6:6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.8","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:8","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\u00c9tienne, plein de gr\u00e2ce et de puissance, faisait des prodiges et de grands miracles parmi le peuple.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.9","name":"Actes 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.7","name":"Actes 6:7","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.9","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:9","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Quelques membres de la synagogue dite des Affranchis, de celle des Cyr\u00e9n\u00e9ens et de celle des Alexandrins, avec des Juifs de Cilicie et d\u2019Asie, se mirent \u00e0 discuter avec lui;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.10","name":"Actes 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.8","name":"Actes 6:8","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.10","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:10","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>mais ils ne pouvaient r\u00e9sister \u00e0 sa sagesse et \u00e0 l\u2019Esprit par lequel il parlait.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.11","name":"Actes 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.9","name":"Actes 6:9","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.11","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:11","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Alors ils suborn\u00e8rent des hommes qui dirent: Nous l\u2019avons entendu prof\u00e9rer des paroles blasph\u00e9matoires contre Mo\u00efse et contre Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.12","name":"Actes 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.10","name":"Actes 6:10","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.12","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:12","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Ils \u00e9murent le peuple, les anciens et les scribes, et, se jetant sur lui, ils le saisirent, et l\u2019emmen\u00e8rent au sanh\u00e9drin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.13","name":"Actes 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.11","name":"Actes 6:11","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.13","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:13","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils produisirent de faux t\u00e9moins, qui dirent: Cet homme ne cesse de prof\u00e9rer des paroles contre le lieu saint et contre la loi;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.14","name":"Actes 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.12","name":"Actes 6:12","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.14","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:14","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.006.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>car nous l\u2019avons entendu dire que J\u00e9sus, ce Nazar\u00e9en, d\u00e9truira ce lieu, et changera les coutumes que Mo\u00efse nous a donn\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.15","name":"Actes 6:15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.13","name":"Actes 6:13","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.15","label":"","reference":"Actes 6:15","prev_osis_id":"Acts.006.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Acts.007.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Acts.6.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Tous ceux qui si\u00e9geaient au sanh\u00e9drin ayant fix\u00e9 les regards sur \u00c9tienne, son visage leur parut comme celui d\u2019un ange.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Acts.6","name":"Actes 6","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.7.1","name":"Actes 7:1","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.7.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Acts.6.14","name":"Actes 6:14","id":"fra-LSG:Acts.6.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.locatio